title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Working Title Addons - Now compatible with su8
description:
In this video we will have a short look at the latest Working Title addons which have been updated to fix some issues including compatibility issues with Sim Update 8.

If you want to try the addons yourself download them via the link below:

Working Title CJ4
https://www.workingtitle.aero/packages/cj4/

Working Title G3000
